strings.id_system_readme:
==ID System==
This bot uses a specialized ID system to classify problems
The general format is as so:

[year][month_name][div_name][q_num]

Parameters:
year->The year of the contest (ex.: 2022)
month_name->strictly 3 letters, allowed types:
 - jan -> January
 - feb -> February
 - opn -> US Open (April)
 - mar -> March
 - dec -> December
 - nov -> November
div_name -> division name, strictly 4 letters, allowed types:
 - gold -> Gold
 - plat -> Platinum
 - silv -> Silver
 - brnz -> Bronze
q_num -> The question number, allowed types: 1,2,3,4

Example usage: 2020decbrnz2 -> USACO 2020 December Bronze Question #2
